	•	Salary Percentage: 50%
	•	Existing Loan EMI: 300 OMR
￼

5. EMI

Logic:
	•	EMI (Equated Monthly Installment) is calculated using the standard EMI formula.

Formula:
￼
Where:
	•	￼ Loan Amount
	•	￼ Monthly Interest Rate (￼)
